quran[12{c,v,t}:
20,65,bolay ke moose ya tum ( apni cheez ) daalo ya hum ( apni cheeze ) pehlay daaltay hain
20,66,moose ne kaha nahi tum hi daalo. ( jab unhon ne cheeze dalain ) to nagahan un ki rasiyaan aur lathyan moose ke khayaal mein aisi anay lagen ke woh ( maidan ) mein idhar udhar daud rahi hain
20,67,( uss waqt ) moose ne apne dil mein khauf maloomkiya
20,68,hum ne kaha khauf nah karo bilashuba tum hi ghalib ho
20,69,aur jo cheez ( yani laathi ) tumahray dahinay haath mein hai usay daal do ke jo kuch unhon ne banaya hai is ko nigal jaye gi. jo kuch unhon ne banaya hai ( yeh to ) gado garonke hthknde hain aur jadugar jahan jaye Falah nahi paye ga
20,70,( al qissa yun hi howa ) to jadugar sjday mein gir parre ( aur ) kehnay lagey ke hum moose aur Haroon ke perwar-digaar par imaan laaye
20,71,( firaon ) bola ke peshtar is ke mein tumhe ijazat dun tum is par imaan le aeye. be shak woh tumhara bara ( yani ustaad ) hai jis ne tum ko jaadoo sikhaya hai. so mein tumahray haath aur paon ( janib ) khilaaf se ktwa dun ga aur khajoor ke tnon par suli chrhhwa dun ga ( is waqt ) tum ko maloom hoga ke hum mein se kis ka azaab ziyada sakht aur der taq rehne wala hai
20,72,unhon ne kaha jo dalail hamaray paas aagaye hain un par aur jis ne hum ko peda hai is par hum aap ko hargiz tarjeeh nahi den ge to aap ko jo hukum dena ho day dijiye. aur aap ( jo ) hukum day satke hain woh sirf isi duniya ki zindagi mein ( day satke hain )
20,73,hum apne perwar-digaar par imaan le aeye taakay woh hamaray gunaaho ko maaf kere aur ( usay bhi ) jo aap ne hum se zabardasti jaadoo karaya. aur khuda behtar aur baqi rehne wala hai
20,74,jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar ke paas gunehgaar ho kar aeye ga to is ke liye jahannum hai. jis mein nah marey ga nah jiye ga
20,75,aur jo is ke rubaroo imandaar ho kar aeye ga aur amal bhi naik kiye hon ge to aisay logon ke liye ounchay ounchay darjay hain
20,76,( yani ) hamesha rehne ke baagh jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain. hamesha un mein rahen ge. aur yeh is shakhs ka badla hai jo pak howa
